a Chaux-de-Fonds]]\n| result     = D\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| round      = Round 10\n| date       = 18 December 1927\n| time       = 14:30\n| team1      = [[FC Concordia Basel|Concordia Basel]]\n| score      = 0 \u2013 1\n| report     = [https://www.fcb-archiv.ch/saison/spiele?command=detail&id=29392 Summary]\n| team2      = [[FC Basel|Basel]]\n| goals1     = \n| goals2     = {{goal|52|pen. 0:1}} [[Alfred Enderlin|Enderlin (I)]]\n| stadium    = [[Landhof]], [[Basel]]\n| attendance = \n| referee    = {{flagicon|SUI}} Demartines [[Lausanne]]\n| result     = W\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| round      = Round 11\n| date       = 22 January 1928\n| time       = 14:3.\n| team1      = [[FC Basel|Basel]]\n| score      = 2 \u2013 1\n| report     = [https://www.fcb-archiv.ch/saison/spiele?command=detail&id=29393 Summary]\n| team2      = [[FC Concordia Basel|Concordia Basel]]\n| goals1     = [[Karl W\u00fcthrich|W\u00fcthrich]] {{goal|1|1:0}}<br />[[Alfred Enderlin|Enderlin (I)]] {{goal|51|2:0}}\n| goals2     = {{goal|61|2:1}} Kielmeyer\n| stadium    = [[Landhof]], [[Basel]]\n| attendance = 1,500\n| referee    = {{flagicon|SUI}} Edm. Dizerens [[Lausanne]]\n| result     = W\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| round      = Round 12\n| date       = 12 February 1928\n| time       = 14:30\n| team1      = [[FC Basel|Basel]]\n| score      = 1 \u2013 2\n| report     = [https://www.fcb-archiv.ch/saison/spiele?command=detail&id=29394 Summary]\n| team2      = [[FC Bern]] \n| goals1     = [[Karl W\u00fcthrich|W\u00fcthrich]] {{goal|41|1:1}}\n| goals2     = {{goal|19|o.g. 0:1}}<br />{{goal|87|1:2}} Brand \n| stadium    = [[Landhof]], [[Basel]]\n| attendance = 1,900\n| referee    = {{flagicon|SUI}} Voisard [[Biel/Bienne]] \n| result     = L\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| round      = Round 13\n| date       = 19 February 1928\n| time       = 15:00\n| team1      = [[FC Basel|Basel]]\n| score      = 4 