 patterns of practice and tools of management.\n\n==== '''L.L.B.''' ====\n\n* Energy Law \n* Criminal Law \n* Labour Law \n* Constitution Law \n* Corporate Law \n* International Trade & Investment Law \n* Banking, Finance & Insurance Law\n* Taxation Law\n* Media & Entertainment Law \n* Legal Compliance and Secretarial Practice \n* Intellectual Property Rights \n* Food, Health & Environment Law \n* Medical and Forensic Law \n* Cyber Law\n\n'''L.L.M.'''\n\n* Energy Law <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.upes.ac.in/course/ll-m-with-specialization-in-energy-law-business-law-international-economic-law-law-technology|title=LLM in Energy {{!}} International Trade {{!}} Commercial & Technology Laws - UPES|website=www.upes.ac.in|language=en|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n\n===== International Economic Law =====\n\n* Law & Technology \n* Business Law\n\n<br />\n\n=== '''School of Engineering'''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.upes.ac.in/schools/school-of-engineering|title=School of Engineering : Best School For Engineering in India {{!}} UPES|website=www.upes.ac.in|language=en|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref> ===\nThe UPES School of Engineering offers several programs including: \u00a0\n\n==== '''Department of Aerospace Engineering''' ====\n\n===== '''UG PROGRAMS''' =====\n\n* B.Tech. (Aerospace Engineering) <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.upes.ac.in/course/b-tech-aerospace-engineering|title=B.Tech. in Aerospace/Aeronautical: Aerospace Engineering Schools Courses and Syllabus {{!}} UPES|website=www.upes.ac.in|language=en|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n* B.Tech. (Aerospace Engineering with specialization in Avionics)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.upes.ac.in/course/b-tech-aerospace-engineering-avionics|title=B.Tech Aeroscope Engineering with Specialization in Avionics {{!}} UPES|website=www.upes.ac.in|language=en|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n\n===== '''PG PROGRAMS''' =====\n\n* M.Tech. (Aerospace Engineering with Unmanned Aerial Vehicle) <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.upes.ac.