ecialization in Industrial & Production Engineering {{!}} UPES|website=www.upes.ac.in|language=en|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n\n===== '''PG PROGRAMS''' =====\n\n* M.Tech (Rotating Equipment) <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.upes.ac.in/course/m-tech-rotating-equipment|title=Rotating Equipment Courses in India - Master in Rotating Equipment {{!}} UPES|website=www.upes.ac.in|language=en|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n\n===== '''DOCTORAL PROGRAMS''' =====\n\n* PhD (Mechanical Engineering) <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.upes.ac.in/course/phd-mechanical-engineering|title=PhD in Mechanical Engineering {{!}} UPES|website=www.upes.ac.in|language=en|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n\n<br />\n\n==== '''Department of Petroleum Engineering and Earth Sciences \u00a0''' ====\n\n===== '''UG PROGRAMS''' =====\n\n* B.Tech. (Applied Petroleum with specialization in Upstream) <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.upes.ac.in/course/b-tech-applied-petroleum-engineering-upstream|title=B. Tech. Petroleum and Upstream Engineering Courses, Syllabus and Scope {{!}} UPES|website=www.upes.ac.in|language=en|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n* B.Tech. (Geo Informatics) <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.upes.ac.in/course/b-tech-geo-informatics-engineering|title=B. Tech. in Geoinformatics Engineering {{!}} Best College For Engineering {{!}} UPES|website=www.upes.ac.in|language=en|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n* B.Tech (Metallurgical and Materials Engineering) <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.upes.ac.in/course/btech-metallurgical-and-materials-engineering|title=B. Tech. Metallurgical & Materials Engineering Courses {{!}} UPES|website=www.upes.ac.in|language=en|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n* B.Tech. (Geo Science Engineering) <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.upes.ac.in/course/btech-geo-science-engineering|title=B.Tech. in Geo Science, Geo Science Engineering Program {{!}} UPES|website=www.upes.ac.in|language=en|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n* B.Tech (Mining Engineering) <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.